OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA warm
OL,6,Fevening with plenty of late sunshine.
OL,7,FStaying largely dry overnight with
OL,8,Fclear periods although patchy low
OL,9,Fcloud may develop, with a chance of
OL,10,Fisolated fog patches inland. Staying
OL,11,Frather warm and humid in coastal
OL,12,Fregions, but cooler inland.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FAny mist rapidly clearing,
OL,15,Fthen often sunny with wispy high cloud
OL,16,Fat times. Fair weather cloud
OL,17,Fdeveloping into the afternoon but
OL,18,Flengthy sunny periods continuing.
OL,19,FBecoming very warm inland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
