OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FSimilar
OL,6,Fon Friday; warm with plenty of
OL,7,Fsunshine. Turning cloudier, breezier
OL,8,Fand somewhat cooler through the
OL,9,Fweekend, and whilst some rain is
OL,10,Fpossible, many places will stay
OL,11,Flargely dry.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
